{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "第十一回 剑道新论\n\n楚留香与胡铁花放走屠狗翁夫妇后，在山巅讨论\"怕老婆\"的话题。楚留香指出屠狗翁惧内是因为爱妻，而非真正害怕。两人回到李玉函家中，李玉函夫妇殷勤相迎，却暗藏杀机。\n\n李玉函引见其父李观鱼——一位垂垂老矣的天下第一剑客。李观鱼面对一柄光彩夺目的宝剑，神情痴迷。李玉函声称父亲有心愿未了，请求楚留香和胡铁花相助。\n\n李观鱼研究剑道数十年，发现武林中最负盛名的剑法并非最精妙的剑法。他以武当\"两仪剑法\"和魔教\"万妙无方慑魂大九式\"为例，说明剑法名气与精妙程度并不成正比。李观鱼又提出\"剑阵\"的问题，指出全真教\"北斗七星阵\"和武当\"八卦剑阵\"虽名动江湖，却难以困住真正的高手。\n\n楚留香与胡铁花渐渐意识到李玉函的请求并非单纯，但碍于礼仪只能继续听下去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你若是我，你难道会杀了他吗?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "一个人若连自己的老婆都怕，他怎么还会有胆子做别的坏事?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你认为他是在受罪，他自己也许却认为是种享受。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "享受?跪算盘、顶夜壶，也能算是享受?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "为什么不能算是享受?杜渔婆会要你顶夜壶么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "当然不会。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "如此说来，她要屠狗翁顶夜壶，就为的是她喜欢他?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错，这就叫爱之深，责之切。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这因为你根本不懂得他们夫妇间的情感。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你懂得?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你以为屠狗翁真的很怕杜渔婆?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那么我问你，他为什么要怕她?你难道看不出屠狗翁的武功要比杜渔婆高得多么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是呀!杜渔婆的身法虽奇诡，但屠狗翁的内力却更深厚，两人若打起来，杜渔婆一定不是屠狗翁的敌手，屠狗翁为什么怕她呢?",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不通不通，你这道理简直不通。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你娶了老婆之后，就知道我这道理通不通了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胡兄原来在梦游虎丘，那一定更有趣了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦!那真有趣极了，只可惜我们并没有做这样的梦，否则大家一齐在梦中相遇，岂非更有趣了!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈等也不敢再打扰前辈了，还是告退吧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位如此仁厚，家父必定感激得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "家父不知是否有什么话要对两位说……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，小弟就先代家父向两位谢过了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这也还是要看看前辈究竟有什么心愿?我们是否有能够效力之处?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这道理小弟自然明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这意思我还是不太懂。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也许是因为江湖中见过这套剑法的人并不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但魔教却一向善门大开，而且一入门就能练剑，武当门下极少出山，魔教子弟却在江湖中横冲直闯，是以无论怎么说?见过这'慑魂大九式'的人，至少也要比见过'两仪剑法'的人多几倍，但'慑魂大九式'却远不．及'两仪剑法'著名，这是为什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒的确是件怪事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这确是件怪事，家父却也想通了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也明白了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这虽然也有道理，但却不是最主要的原因。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦!那么最主要的原因是什么呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我方才说的，岂非就是这意思吗?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魔教子弟并非剑法不精，而是他们的心术不正，行事太邪，所以和人动手时，就不能理直气壮，所以他们的剑法就算比别人高，也难免落败，",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贤伉俪认为在下说的是否还有些道理?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但一个人只有在知道自己做的事是对的时候，才会有必胜的信心，是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这件事我也听说过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剑阵?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖高手死在武当剑客中手里的并不少，但却没有一人死在'八卦剑阵'里，这件事胡兄难道不觉得有些奇怪么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是这'八卦剑阵'迎战高手时，却偏偏变得无效了，武林中简直就没有一种绝对有效的剑阵，这是为什么呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剑阵纵有破绽，但普天之下，无论哪一种剑法也都难免有破绽的，那么，八人联手的剑阵，为什么还不如一人使出的剑法有效呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这原因令尊难道也想通了么?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    }
  ],
